---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service - Empire Inc"
  description="Terms of Service for Empire Inc mobile application"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Terms of Service for Empire Inc</h1>
      
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8">
        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 7, 2026
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By downloading, installing, or using Empire Inc ("App"), you agree to these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree, do not use the App.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p>
            Empire Inc is a business simulation game where you build and manage virtual businesses, investments, and lifestyle items to grow your empire.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. User Accounts</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">3.1 Account Creation</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>You must provide accurate information when creating an account</li>
            <li>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account</li>
            <li>You must be at least 13 years old to use the App</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">3.2 Account Termination</h3>
          <p>We may suspend or terminate your account if you:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Violate these Terms</li>
            <li>Engage in fraudulent activity</li>
            <li>Abuse the App or other users</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Virtual Items and Currency</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">4.1 Virtual Economy</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>All virtual currency, items, and businesses exist only within the App</li>
            <li>Virtual items have no real-world monetary value</li>
            <li>Virtual progress cannot be exchanged for real currency</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">4.2 Purchases</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>In-app purchases are processed through Apple App Store or Google Play Store</li>
            <li>All purchases are final and non-refundable (except as required by law)</li>
            <li>Subscription terms are governed by the respective app store policies</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Subscriptions</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">5.1 Premium Plans</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Premium subscriptions provide enhanced features and ad-free experience</li>
            <li>Subscriptions auto-renew unless cancelled before the renewal date</li>
            <li>Cancel through your App Store or Google Play account settings</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">5.2 Pricing</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Prices are displayed in the App and may vary by region</li>
            <li>We reserve the right to modify pricing with notice</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. User Conduct</h2>
          <p>You agree NOT to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Use cheats, exploits, or automation software</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to the App</li>
            <li>Harass, abuse, or harm other users</li>
            <li>Impersonate others or provide false information</li>
            <li>Use the App for illegal purposes</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">7.1 Our Rights</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Empire Inc and all content are owned by us or our licensors</li>
            <li>You may not copy, modify, or distribute our content</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">7.2 Your Rights</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>You retain rights to any feedback you provide</li>
            <li>You grant us license to use your feedback to improve the App</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">8. Disclaimers</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">8.1 No Warranty</h3>
          <p>THE APP IS PROVIDED "AS IS" WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND.</p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">8.2 Limitation of Liability</h3>
          <p>WE ARE NOT LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, OR CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">9. Indemnification</h2>
          <p>
            You agree to indemnify us against claims arising from your use of the App or violation of these Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">10. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We may modify these Terms at any time. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">11. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms are governed by applicable laws. Disputes will be resolved in accordance with applicable jurisdiction.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">12. Contact</h2>
          <p>For questions about these Terms:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:legal@empireinc.app" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">legal@empireinc.app</a></li>
            <li>Website: <a href="https://empireinc.app" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">https://empireinc.app</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800">
        <p class="text-slate-400">Empire Inc</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

